title: District 11 girls tennis 2015 singles finals set
text:
Elessa Jacobs of Easton is into the final of the District 11 Class AAA singles tournament. (Courtesy Photo) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 09, 2015 2:06 AM, updated October 09, 2015 5:43 PM 
The championship matches for the District 11 Class AAA and AA girls tennis singles tournaments have been set. 
It will be the top two seeds in each bracket playing for the gold. 
The Class AAA final features top-seeded Nina DeLuna of Southern Lehigh against No. 2 seed Elessa Jacobs of Easton . It will be played at 12:30 p.m. Monday at Lehigh University. 
In Class AA, No. 1 seed Tyra Ott of Wilson will play second-seeded Coco Chen of Notre Dame in the finals at 2 p.m. Monday at Lehigh University.
